; The 3D Cosmetics / skin-selection screen. The root is a Node3D world (rendered straight to the
; window) and cosmetics.gd builds the whole diorama + the CanvasLayer UI overlay in code (the
; home_screen pattern; graveyard rule = no hand-authored rotated transforms). Reached from the
; main-menu COSMETICS button (menu_flow.gd); BACK returns to home_screen.tscn.
[gd_scene load_steps=2 format=3]

